1. Install Tensorflow.
2. Train language model
python ~/ptb_word_lm.py --data_path=dataciv --file_prefix=charciv --seed_for_sample="move settler resource" --model=charlarge --save_path=resultciv-char
3. Sampling from the model
python ~/ptb_word_lm.py --data_path=dataciv --file_prefix=charciv --seed_for_sample="move settler resource" --model=charlarge --save_path=resultciv-char --sample_mode=True

============================
python version: 2.7
Tensorflow version: Ubuntu/Linux 64-bit, CPU only, Python 2.7
	   	    tensorflow_gpu-0.12.0rc0-cp27-none-linux_x86_64.whl